character.title: A quiet  person with a lot of hidden personality
character.name: Fan
character.description: A thinking, quiet, and private  person who can sometimes live in his own mind and doesn’t show everyone his identity . Doesn’t like excluding things like how famous you are,  how much money you have, or what race you are. Is a kind and advice giving to his friend and often has deep emotions and thoughts
